        "2 cups rolled oats",
        "1 cup chopped nuts",
        "1/2 cup candied orange peel or orange zest"
      ],
      "instructions": [
        "Sift together flour, baking soda, and salt.",
        "Cream shortening with white and brown sugars until light.",
        "Beat in eggs and vanilla.",
